{"type":"message","id":"91b1a281","parentId":"39557a1a","timestamp":"2026-04-06T11:35:01.446Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8o9GMzgfLGV0OL6T0z6GWDdd|fc_0decf3a63c3e6dc30169d39a641ef48197844b4e3c7fbe063f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Classificador semantico canonico. Julgamento LLM real.\nNao copiar classificacao preliminary do worker.\nAvaliar todos os candidates em um unico pass.\nDisco e verdade. Schema e contract.\nNao fazer discovery nem coverage.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775475301434}}
{"type":"message","id":"155c3142","parentId":"91b1a281","timestamp":"2026-04-06T11:35:01.455Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_6UNBVrT35xuYtZ1zrKTPIVCX|fc_0decf3a63c3e6dc30169d39a641f008197be93556c67d53100","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775475301446}}
