 \"visual_reference\",\n      \"target_fitness_note\": \"Direct portrait of Eurico Gaspar Dutra; extremely on-target for a historical person reference.\",\n      \"downstream_usefulness_note\": \"Strong for visual matching, identity confirmation, and scene reference planning.\",\n      \"asset_usability_note\": \"The source title indicates a portrait and the asset appears directly relevant; usable as reference-only.\",\n      \"is_best_candidate\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"candidate_id\": \"c002\",\n      \"final_classification\": \"factual_evidence\",\n      \"target_fitness_note\": \"Explicitly identifies Eurico Gaspar Dutra as President of the United States of Brazil; excellent factual anchor.\",\n      \"downstream_usefulness_note\": \"Useful for biographical verification and captioning, but less useful than a direct portrait for visual reference.\",\n      \"asset_usability_note\": \"High-confidence reference record from a reputable library source; usable for factual corroboration.\",\n      \"is_best_candidate\": true\n    },\n    {\n      \"candidate_id\": \"c003\",\n      \"final_classification\": \"factual_evidence\",\n      \"target_fitness_note\": \"Matches the target entity and supplies concise biographical context.\",\n      \"downstream_usefulness_note\": \"Useful as a supporting factual source, though it is secondary to direct archival or library records.\",\n      \"asset_usability_note\": \"Usable as reference-only biographical context; not a primary visual asset.\",\n      \"is_best_candidate\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"candidate_id\": \"c004\",\n      \"final_classification\": \"factual_evidence\",\n      \"target_fitness_note\": \"Biographical page for Eurico Gaspar Dutra with historical details that align with the target identity.\",\n      \"downstream_usefulness_note\": \"Good supporting evidence for era, role, and background, but not a visual asset.\",\n      \"asset_usability_note\": \"Usable as reference-only factual background; suitable for corroboration.\",\n      \"is_best_candidate\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"candidate_id\": \"c005\",\n      \"final_classification\": \"factual_evidence\",\n      \"target_fitness_note\": \"Highly relevant to Dutra's presidency and policy context, including gambling prohibition mentioned in the brief topic.\",\n      \"downstream_usefulness_note\": \"Especially useful for contextual writing around the historical period and the political climate.\",\n      \"asset_usability_note\": \"Usable as reference-only contextual evidence; no visual utility.\",\n      \"is_best_candidate\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"candidate_id\": \"c006\",\n      \"final_classification\": \"factual_evidence\",\n      \"target_fitness_note\": \"Solid biographical match from Britannica, confirming the person and his presidential role.\",\n      \"downstream_usefulness_note\": \"Reliable supporting source for general biography and era context.\",\n      \"asset_usability_note\": \"Usable as reference-only factual background; no visual asset.\",\n      \"is_best_candidate\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"candidate_id\": \"c007\",\n      \"final_classification\": \"factual_evidence\",\n      \"target_fitness_note\": \"Dedicated biography page for Eurico Gaspar Dutra; clearly aligned to the target.\",\n      \"downstream_usefulness_note\": \"Useful supplementary factual source, especially for structured biographical lookup.\",\n      \"asset_usability_note\": \"Usable as reference-only factual background.\",\n      \"is_best_candidate\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"candidate_id\": \"c008\",\n      \"final_classification\": \"factual_evidence\",\n      \"target_fitness_note\": \"Directly about Marshal Eurico Gaspar Dutra, confirming the military biography.\",\n      \"downstream_usefulness_note\": \"Helpful for historical and military context, but weaker than the more authoritative or richer sources above.\",\n      \"asset_usability_note\": \"Usable as reference-only factual background.\",\n      \"is_best_candidate\": false\n    }\n  ],\n  \"best_candidate_ids\": [\n    \"c001\",\n    \"c002\"\n  ],\n  \"evaluator_notes\": [\n    \"No rejects: all candidates are semantically aligned with Eurico Gaspar Dutra.\",\n    \"c001 is the strongest visual reference; c002 is the strongest library-style factual record.\",\n    \"The rest are supporting factual sources and can be retained for corroboration and context.\"\n  ],\n  \"warnings\": []\n}"},"partialJson":"{\"path\":\"C:\\\\Users\\\\User-OEM\\\\Desktop\\\\content-factory\\\\auto_content_factory\\\\data\\\\006_pt\\\\o_quitandinha_ia_ser_o_maior_casino_do_mundo_-_o_brasil_proibiu_o_jogo_2_anos_depois_de_inaugurar\\\\b2\\\\sectors\\\\s4_asset_research\\\\targets\\\\t002\\\\t002_evaluated_candidate_set.json\",\"content\":\"{\\n  \\\"contract_version\\\": \\\"s4.evaluated_candidate_set.v1\\\",\\n  \\\"target_id\\\": \\\"t002\\\",\\n  \\\"canonical_label\\\": \\\"Eurico Gaspar Dutra\\\",\\n  \\\"target_type\\\": \\\"person_historical\\\",\\n  \\\"scene_ids\\\": [\\n    \\\"scene_026\\\",\\n    \\\"scene_034\\\",\\n    \\\"scene_035\\\",\\n    \\\"scene_036\\\",\\n    \\\"scene_107\\\",\\n    \\\"scene_108\\\",\\n    \\\"scene_124\\\",\\n    \\\"scene_127\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"evaluated_candidates\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"candidate_id\\\": \\\"c001\\\",\\n      \\\"final_classification\\\": \\\"visual_reference\\\",\\n      \\\"target_fitness_note\\\": \\\"Direct portrait of Eurico Gaspar Dutra; extremely on-target for a historical person reference.\\\",\\n      \\\"downstream_usefulness_note\\\": \\\"Strong for visual matching, identity confirmation, and scene reference planning.\\\",\\n      \\\"asset_usability_note\\\": \\\"The source title indicates a portrait and the asset appears directly relevant; usable as reference-only.\\\",\\n      \\\"is_best_candidate\\\": true\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"candidate_id\\\": \\\"c002\\\",\\n      \\\"final_classification\\\": \\\"factual_evidence\\\",\\